Package org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.datamanager.server.spring

Class APIManagerResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.datamanager.server.spring.APIManagerResource
  • @RestController
@RequestMapping("/servers/{serverName}/open-metadata/access-services/data-manager/users/{userId}")
public class APIManagerResource
extends java.lang.Object
    APIManagerResource is the server-side implementation of the Data Manager OMAS's support for APIs. It matches the APIManagerClient.
